'''Agemmay amaziɣ aɛṛab''' d yiwen ugemmay ig ttwaxdamen i tira n [[Tamaziɣt]] s ugemmay aɛṛab. Yebda yettwaxdam di lqarn 8 ama d lqarn 19. Urğin deg umezruy ittwanoti labuda aṭaṣ n'leɛruc ig gumman ad arun, ḥaca deg zawaya, andi lecyux ttarun lecɛur d'tefsir ig ttwaterğmen s tmaziɣt. Ass-a, ulac tamurt isexdamen agemmay agi, [[Lmeruk]] ttexdam [[Tifinaɣ]], ama d [[Lezzayer]], tettxedem agemmay alaṭini.
